org.cougaar.core.service
Interface AppletService

All Superinterfaces:
Service
public interface AppletService
extends Service

This service provides access to Applet methods, and is only available if the node was launched from within a browser Applet.

There are dozens of Applet methods, including all methods defined in AWT "Component". For now we support the basic methods and can add more in the future as required.
